body_html: I mean load average as reported by e.g. top or uptime and many other tools. For example, here is an article that explains load and how it is different from CPU utilization: http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/9001. You can find people reporting similar problems by googling "high load average low cpu".

body: I mean load average as reported by e.g. `top` or `uptime` and many other tools. For example, here is an article that explains load and how it is different from CPU utilization: http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/9001. You can find people reporting similar problems by googling "high load average low cpu".
